definition: to brave it out/to the bitter end

sentences.english: Think about it: who needs whom?
sentences.chinese: 想想，到底是誰離不開誰？

sentences.english: After all, this is male chauvinism at play in.
sentences.chinese: 說到底，這也是大男人主義在作怪了。

sentences.english: Bottle-feeding lets me know how much nutrition the baby has had.
sentences.chinese: 瓶喂使我知道寶寶到底吸收了多少營養。

sentences.english: What is the point of our bad conscience?
sentences.chinese: 我們的錯誤的良知到底是爲了什麼？
那這三觀亭到底是哪三觀啊？

sentences.english: I'd love to send a probe in there to find out what's really going on.
sentences.chinese: 我很想送一個探測器去那裏，看看到底發生了什麼。

sentences.english: What advantage melanism brings in these circumstances is obscure.
sentences.chinese: 在這些環境中表皮黑化到底有什麼優勢似乎模糊不清。

sentences.english: Stop defeusinging regarding the bush. Will you quit or not?
sentences.chinese: 別拐彎兒抹角了，你到底戒不戒菸？

sentences.english: Lady in the end how to be beautiful like?
sentences.chinese: 女人到底怎麼樣纔算美麗？

sentences.english: What was the tributary system and how will it shape China's future behaviour?
sentences.chinese: 到底什麼是納貢體制，它將使中國成爲什麼樣的國家？

sentences.english: The liberals prefer to sit on the fence while the other parties fight it out.
sentences.chinese: 自由黨寧可抱騎牆態度，坐待其他黨派去鬥爭到底。

sentences.english: Now...who in the hell understands men?
sentences.chinese: 現在，到底有誰瞭解男人這東西？

sentences.english: What on earth humiliates the image of "students studying abroad"?
sentences.chinese: 到底是什麼損害了“留學生”的品牌形象？
到底這種知識所爲爲何？

sentences.english: Japan's new government Poodle or Pekinese?
sentences.chinese: 日本新政府到底是獅子狗還是京巴？

sentences.english: So how much exercise should the average person be getting?
sentences.chinese: 那對於一般人而言，到底要進行多少體育運動呢？
